Package: dplyrmongodb
Type: Package
Title: A grammar of data manipulation on MongoDB motivated by the plyr and dplyr packages
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2014-01-29
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Imports: rmongodb, dplyr
Author: Markus Schmidberger (mongosoup.de)
Maintainer: Markus Schmidberger <markus@mongosoup.de>
Description: A fast, consistent tool for working with data frame like objects in MongoDB (www.mongodb.org).
License: Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/schmidb/dplyrmongodb
BugReports: https://github.com/schmidb/dplyrmongodb/issues 
SystemRequirements: MongoDB
Suggests: RUnit
